<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/117811-can-a-7th-grader-read-the-book-in-a-few">can a 7th grader read the book in a few days or a week</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_117811'><a id="like_count_community_question_117811" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/117811?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F5308.The_Pearl">like</a></span>

