  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2906291116?book_show_action=true">Jul 22, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Swaroop" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Swaroop" href="/user/show/100264072-swaroop">Swaroop</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2906291116" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14484963987850818032"><i>&quot;In the town they tell the story of the great pearl - how it was found and how it was lost again...&quot;</i><br/><br/>An amazing piece of literature!!<br/><br/>Beautiful words!<br/><br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/585.John_Steinbeck' title='John Steinbeck' rel='nofollow noopener'>John Steinbeck</a>&apos;s <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5308.The_Pearl' title='The Pearl by John Steinbeck' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Pearl</a> is a simple story about simple people, with beautiful words. <br/><br/>A <b>must-read!</b></span>
  <span id="freeText14484963987850818032" style="display:none"><i>"In the town they tell the story of the great pearl - how it was found and how it was lost again..."</i><br /><br />An amazing piece of literature!!<br /><br />Beautiful words!<br /><br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/585.John_Steinbeck" title="John Steinbeck" rel="nofollow noopener">John Steinbeck</a>'s <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5308.The_Pearl" title="The Pearl by John Steinbeck" rel="nofollow noopener">The Pearl</a> is a simple story about simple people, with beautiful words. <br /><br />A <b>must-read!</b></span>
